<paragraph base="F55666774" id="IFRS17_107"><paranum>107</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 17"/><data name="paranum" value="107"/></prolog><body><bodydiv base="IFRS2020-3">     <p id="IFRS17_P0439">For <xref base="F55666957" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0532">insurance contracts<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0186"/></ph></xref> other than those to which the premium allocation approach described in <xref base="F59235603" href="IFRS17_g53-59.dita#IFRS17_g53-59/IFRS17_g53-59_TI" id="IFRS17_X0472">paragraphs 53&#x2013;59</xref> or <xref base="F59235608" href="IFRS17_g69-70.dita#IFRS17_g69-70/IFRS17_g69-70_TI" id="IFRS17_X0473">69&#x2013;70A</xref> has been applied, an entity shall disclose the effect on the statement of financial position separately for insurance contracts issued and <xref base="F55667022" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0554">reinsurance contracts<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0323"/></ph></xref> held that are initially recognised in the period, showing their effect at initial recognition on: </p>     <ol base="F55666776" type="lower-alpha" id="IFRS17_L0081"><li id="IFRS17_107_a"><li_value>(a)</li_value>         <p base="F55666777" id="IFRS17_P0440">the estimates of the present value of future cash outflows, showing separately the amount of the <xref base="F55666953" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0531">insurance acquisition cash flows<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0184"/></ph></xref>;</p>       </li><li id="IFRS17_107_b"><li_value>(b)</li_value>         <p base="F55666779" id="IFRS17_P0441">the estimates of the present value of future cash inflows;</p>       </li><li id="IFRS17_107_c"><li_value>(c)</li_value>         <p base="F55666781" id="IFRS17_P0442">the <xref base="F55667026" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0555">risk adjustment for non-financial risk<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0343"/></ph></xref>; and</p>       </li><li id="IFRS17_107_d"><li_value>(d)</li_value>         <p base="F55666783" id="IFRS17_P0443">the <xref base="F55666917" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0519">contractual service margin<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0052"/></ph></xref>.</p>       </li></ol>     </bodydiv></body></paragraph>